      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver release notes and version control records confirm reproducibility of simulation results.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2021 R2 used under institutional software quality management plan. Version-controlled case files archived in institutional repository. Release notes reviewed; no known defects affecting rotating-frame turbulence treatment."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
